Package net.hudup.core.data.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UnitTable
    This class represents a table for showing data in a unit.
    UnitTable.SelectionChangedListener
    This interface is used to response to a selection changed event.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataConfigTextField
    Text field to show data configuration.
    DataDriverComboBox
    This graphic user interface (GUI) component shows a combo box for users to select a data driver represented by DataDriver class.
    DataDriverListTable
    This graphic user interface (GUI) component as a table shows a list of data drivers (DataDriverList).
    DatasetParserComboBox
    This graphic user interface (GUI) component shows a combo box for users to select a dataset parser DatasetParser.
    ProfileTable
    This class is table for showing a collection of profiles.
    PropDlg
    The graphic user interface (GUI) component as a dialog shows a properties list represented by PropList.
    PropPane
    The graphic user interface (GUI) component as panel JPanel shows a properties list represented by PropList.
    PropTable
    The graphic user interface (GUI) component as table JTable shows a properties list represented by PropList.
    SysConfigPane
    The graphic user interface (GUI) component as panel JPanel shows a system properties list represented by SysConfig.
    UnitComboBox
    The graphic user interface (GUI) component as combo box JList shows the UnitList.
    UnitListBox
    The graphic user interface (GUI) component as list box JList shows the UnitList.
    UnitTable.SelectionChangedEvent
    This class represents an event when selection is changed.
    UnitTextField
    Text field to store a unit.
